Plans for 0.5.0
===============

  * General
      - Use "." as decimal for time
      - Move developer specific options to under test dir?
      - Move variables from application and project to delegates
      - Raise exceptions instead of returning None or False
      - Get rid of logger?
      - Use class variables and refer to them as self.var
          - gaupol.base.files
      - Use relib.NONE instead of None in flags?
